      <event start="T926-713" end="T927-743">in vsega boga. </event>
      <event start="T927-743" end="T931-626">Sting iz ork() sr() v simfoničnem orkestru v Zagrebu. </event>
      <event start="T932-618" end="T934-504">To je zato, k sva šla v Zagreb, </event>
      <event start="T934-504" end="T937-731">in v Zagrebu so naredili v areni zvok, </event>
      <event start="T938-226" end="T530">so naredili akustiko </event>
      <event start="T530" end="T323">in to tako, </event>
      <event start="T323" end="T324">razumeš, </event>
      <event start="T324" end="T325">to je čudovito, </event>
      <event start="T325" end="T326">glej, </event>
      <event start="T326" end="T942-504">to, to se, to se zvok razlije, </event>
      <event start="T942-504" end="T327">razumeš, </event>
      <event start="T327" end="T328">ne odbija se, </event>
      <event start="T328" end="T947-133">lepo se absorbira, </event>
      <event start="T947-133" end="T948-0">l() glej, </event>
      <event start="T948-0" end="T329">gre, </event>
      <event start="T329" end="T330">ne. </event>
      <event start="T330" end="T331">Še Bor Tros je bil tam, </event>
      <event start="T331" end="T332">ne. </event>
      <event start="T332" end="T333">Se ga spomniš? </event>
      <event start="T333" end="T531">Antončičev Bor, </event>
      <event start="T531" end="T334">k je rekel: </event>
      <event start="T334" end="T335">"Glej, </event>
      <event start="T335" end="T336">to, to, to je noro," </event>
      <event start="T336" end="T953-41">ne. </event>
      <event start="T953-816" end="T337">Noro, kakšen zvok, </event>
      <event start="T337" end="T338">ne. </event>
      <event start="T338" end="T339">Sem rekel: </event>
      <event start="T339" end="T955-886">"Glej, </event>
      <event start="T955-886" end="T340">pri nama je že tulele na tribuni," </event>
      <event start="T340" end="T532">veš, </event>
      <event start="T532" end="T958-814">k sva bila majčkeno desno, </event>
      <event start="T958-814" end="T959-782">ne. </event>
      <event start="T959-782" end="T341">Eee znači, </event>
      <event start="T341" end="T342">in je potem eee je bil to res ... </event>
      <event start="T342" end="T343">Pol se, pol je bil pa čez, </event>
      <event start="T343" end="T345">ne vem, koliko, </event>
      <event start="T345" end="T967-443">par mesecev ali par tednov </event>
      <event start="T967-741" end="T968-251">v </event>
      <event start="T968-251" end="T969-043">Ljubljani. </event>
      <event start="T969-618" end="T971-024">In [nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T971-024" end="T972-012">Je bilo pa zanič. </event>
      <event start="T972-254" end="T973-499">Je bilo pa za nikamor ni bilo. </event>
      <event start="T992-236" end="T994-661">Tisto je denarja zmanjkalo za tisti projekt in </event>
      <event start="T994-661" end="T350">je bilo pol niso takoj. </event>
      <event start="T350" end="T351">In je še zdaj, še zdaj, </event>
      <event start="T351" end="T353">se spomniš, k smo na Stinge, </event>
      <event start="T353" end="T1001-183">sva bila na Stingoti eee lani? </event>
      <event start="T1001-718" end="T354">Iz Three Point Oh, </event>
      <event start="T354" end="T1003-303">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1003-692" end="T355">Je bil samo z dvema, </event>
      <event start="T355" end="T356">pa tako, </event>
      <event start="T356" end="T1006-563">ne, </event>
      <event start="T1006-563" end="T1008-743">malo [nerazumljivo] matrice zraven. </event>
      <event start="T1008-743" end="T1009-615">Eee </event>
      <event start="T1009-615" end="T357">je bil dober zvok, </event>
      <event start="T357" end="T1011-101">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1011-927" end="T358">Ampak ne pa tudi vrhunski, </event>
      <event start="T358" end="T1014-532">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1014-532" end="T359">Ampak je bil pa dober, </event>
      <event start="T359" end="T1016-157">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1016-157" end="T1019-129">Se pravi veliko je odvisno tudi same muzike, ampak ... </event>
      <event start="T1023-925" end="T1024-45">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1027-64" end="T1028-016">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T1028-016" end="T1028-472">je to že v šundri, </event>
      <event start="T1028-472" end="T1029-276">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1042-464" end="T1043-063">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T1047-244" end="T1047-977">Ne, ne. </event>
      <event start="T1048-611" end="T373">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T373" end="T1049-856">saj pravim. </event>
      <event start="T1054-836" end="T1055-966">Yeah. </event>
      <event start="T1062-923" end="T1065-796">Pa se spomniš, kdaj s(), kva smo še delali v Zagrebu? </event>
      <event start="T1068-273" end="T381">To ne, </event>
      <event start="T381" end="T383">ampak smo pa šli še na Watersa, </event>
      <event start="T383" end="T382">na The Wall, </event>
      <event start="T382" end="T1071-95">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1082-906" end="T1084-274">K je bilo pol dvorane prazne. </event>
      <event start="T1110-207" end="T1111-396">Ooo eee ... </event>
      <event start="T1112-208" end="T1113-536">To je bilo tudi, </event>
      <event start="T1113-536" end="T1114-923">animacije, vse tisto. </event>
      <event start="T1115-665" end="T1116-615">Tako da to so ... </event>
      <event start="T1117-947" end="T1118-779">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1120-182" end="T399">Šov je bil ta pravi, </event>
      <event start="T399" end="T1121-851">en najboljših. </event>
      <event start="T1122-08" end="T400">Ni čudno, da je The Wall že štirideset let en najboljših šovov, </event>
      <event start="T400" end="T1127-114">ali pa petinštirideset let. </event>
      <event start="T1127-114" end="T1129-455">Ne, ne, je produkcija bila. </event>
      <event start="T1131-458" end="T1132-368">In je bilo ... </event>
      <event start="T1132-368" end="T1133-474">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1133-474" end="T402">Eee dobro, </event>
      <event start="T402" end="T403">na Maidenih je bilo tudi solidno, </event>
      <event start="T403" end="T1136-513">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1141-043" end="T1141-942">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T1151-226" end="T1151-869">Tudi tam? </event>
      <event start="T1154-614" end="T1154-98">Ja? </event>
      <event start="T1172-615" end="T417">Mislim, </event>
      <event start="T417" end="T418">glej, </event>
      <event start="T418" end="T419">počutiš se lahko dobro kjerkoli, </event>
      <event start="T419" end="T420">to je, to je čisto subjektivno, </event>
      <event start="T420" end="T1181-181">ampak eni koncerti imajo preprosto preveliko gnečo </event>
      <event start="T1181-181" end="T1184-656">in je ta faktor nelagodja večji od, </event>
      <event start="T1184-656" end="T421">razumeš, </event>
      <event start="T421" end="T1187-878">tistega, da, da ti nekaj paše muzika </event>
      <event start="T1187-878" end="T422">in da ti hočeš doživeti nekaj čudovitega, prekrasnega, </event>
      <event start="T422" end="T1191-170">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1191-794" end="T1192-396">To je ta, </event>
      <event start="T1192-396" end="T423">to je ta paradoks, k ga v teh velikih eee stampedih, </event>
      <event start="T423" end="T424">da ne rečem, </event>
      <event start="T424" end="T1198-293">eee doživiš </event>
      <event start="T1198-293" end="T425">in pol se moraš nekako nekako sam s sabo zmeniti. </event>
      <event start="T425" end="T536">Ali ti paše, da te malo scat, </event>
      <event start="T536" end="T537">da ti malo ono, </event>
      <event start="T537" end="T538">da ti je gužva, </event>
      <event start="T538" end="T1206-595">da te tam rinejo ljudje </event>
      <event start="T1206-595" end="T426">pa da še zmeraj znaš uživati, </event>
      <event start="T426" end="T1208-596">ne, </event>
      <event start="T1208-596" end="T1209-112">ali ti pa to prevaga, </event>
      <event start="T1209-112" end="T427">razumeš, </event>
      <event start="T427" end="T428">pa rečeš pol: </event>
      <event start="T428" end="T430">"Nikoli več ne grem na tak koncert," </event>
      <event start="T430" end="T1213-796">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1213-796" end="T1216-323">Tako da to je, to je, to je mmm ... </event>
      <event start="T1216-323" end="T431">Zato verjetno veliko ljudi ne hodi na koncerte, ker ne mara gužve, </event>
      <event start="T431" end="T432">ne. </event>
      <event start="T432" end="T1220-583">Mislim, to je ... </event>
      <event start="T1220-583" end="T433">A veš. </event>
      <event start="T433" end="T434">Kar je več kot deset tavžent ljudi na kupu, </event>
      <event start="T434" end="T435">ne, </event>
      <event start="T435" end="T436">je je je kar, je kar zajebano, </event>
      <event start="T436" end="T1226-151">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1226-151" end="T1227-360">Sploh če nisi na tribuni, </event>
      <event start="T1227-360" end="T1228-331">zato smo mi </event>
      <event start="T1228-708" end="T437">zadnje cajte, </event>
      <event start="T437" end="T438">razumeš, </event>
      <event start="T438" end="T1233-444">skoraj večkrat se r() abonirali za tribune. </event>
      <event start="T1235-439" end="T1236-371">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1239-6" end="T1240-591">Tako, tako. </event>
      <event start="T1240-965" end="T1241-393">Tako. </event>
      <event start="T1245-822" end="T1246-484">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T1247-008" end="T1247-503">Tako. </event>
      <event start="T1252-477" end="T439">Ti, </event>
      <event start="T439" end="T541">kva je pa bilo, kva, </event>
      <event start="T541" end="T1258-622">kako se ti je pa zdelo u tamle u, na Dunaju, k smo šli na Blinke? </event>
      <event start="T1264-778" end="T1265-259">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1266-726" end="T442">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T442" end="T1268-172">tudi jaz. </event>
      <event start="T1275-94" end="T1276-867">Ja ja. </event>
      <event start="T1289-81" end="T448">Tudi meni se dvorana ni dopadla, </event>
      <event start="T448" end="T1293-441">tudi nismo imeli najboljše pozicije, </event>
      <event start="T1293-441" end="T449">po mojem, </event>
      <event start="T449" end="T1294-432">ampak ... </event>
      <event start="T1295-066" end="T1295-68">Glej, pač. </event>
      <event start="T1296-799" end="T1299-067">Bolj, bolj smo bili odzgoraj, </event>
      <event start="T1299-067" end="T451">ne, </event>
      <event start="T451" end="T1299-784">tako da tam je tudi že, </event>
      <event start="T1299-784" end="T1302-392">tam se tudi že zvok drugače eee razliva. </event>
      <event start="T1303-188" end="T1304-889">Ampak eem ... </event>
      <event start="T1304-889" end="T453">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T453" end="T542">fajn, da smo jih videli, </event>
      <event start="T542" end="T1307-528">k so, to so bile naše srednješolske sanje, </event>
      <event start="T1307-528" end="T1309-09">ne, </event>
      <event start="T1309-09" end="T1311-055">pravzaprav. </event>
      <event start="T1311-055" end="T1315-201">In smo pol to majčkeno iz eee iz() [nerazumljivo]. </event>
      <event start="T1319-587" end="T1319-944">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1333-961" end="T1334-609">Ta mala sploh še jih nikoli ni, nikoli zares poslušala </event>
      <event start="T1334-609" end="T1338-378">in se je kar odločila, da jih ne mara. </event>
      <event start="T1338-378" end="T543">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T543" end="T459">to, to ne sme se tako. </event>
      <event start="T459" end="T1340-855">To ne smeš otroke tako vzgajati, </event>
      <event start="T1340-855" end="T460">razumeš, </event>
      <event start="T460" end="T1342-559">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1343-487" end="T1343-842">Je() ()beštrga, </event>
      <event start="T1343-842" end="T1344-98">to ni dobro, </event>
      <event start="T1344-98" end="T1345-799">glej. </event>
      <event start="T1345-799" end="T461">To se mora otrok sam odločiti. </event>
      <event start="T461" end="T462">Mislim, </event>
      <event start="T462" end="T463">glej, </event>
      <event start="T463" end="T464">to je, to je prekrasno, če lahko otrok sam reče: </event>
      <event start="T464" end="T1351-128">"Daj mi en komad," </event>
      <event start="T1351-128" end="T1352-396">razumeš, </event>
      <event start="T1352-396" end="T466">"tako bolj žestoki," </event>
      <event start="T466" end="T467">ne. </event>
      <event start="T467" end="T468">Jaz bom, jaz tudi svoji ta mali rečem: </event>
      <event start="T468" end="T469">"Glej, </event>
      <event start="T469" end="T470">če ti kaj paše, </event>
      <event start="T470" end="T471">razumeš, </event>
      <event start="T471" end="T472">samo povej, </event>
      <event start="T472" end="T473">glej, </event>
      <event start="T473" end="T474">bomo vse zrihtali," </event>
      <event start="T474" end="T1359-027">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1359-027" end="T475">Zadnje cajte najbolj ima rada muzikal od Lion Kinga, </event>
      <event start="T475" end="T1362-238">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1364-380" end="T1365-926">Veš, kako so pele v avtu. </event>
      <event start="T1365-926" end="T1367-228">Aaj. </event>
      <event start="T1367-228" end="T478">Jah, </event>
      <event start="T478" end="T1368-966">pele so skup. </event>
      <event start="T1368-966" end="T1370-508">Circle of Life pa tako. </event>
      <event start="T1370-508" end="T1371-201">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1378-017" end="T484">To ga pa ni, </event>
      <event start="T484" end="T1380-809">ne. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T1385-718" end="T1387-247">Po mojem je, je to, </event>
      <event start="T1387-247" end="T1388-551">bom rekel ... </event>
      <event start="T1392-259" end="T1392-772">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1394-576" end="T488">Pa ja, </event>
      <event start="T488" end="T1399-787">saj je še bil kak koncert oziroma lokal(), lokalni so sigurno še bili, </event>
      <event start="T1399-787" end="T1401-362">ne eee .... </event>
      <event start="T1401-362" end="T1404-096">Ampak eee ja. </event>
      <event start="T1404-096" end="T1407-654">Hala Tivoli Seal dva osem. </event>
      <event start="T1409-004" end="T490">Tako, </event>
      <event start="T490" end="T491">no, </event>
      <event start="T491" end="T492">tudi plac sam za koncerte bolj tako, </event>
      <event start="T492" end="T493">no, </event>
      <event start="T493" end="T1412-952">ampak, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1413-963" end="T494">Smo šli. </event>
      <event start="T494" end="T1416-38">Pa jaz sem bil na Juliu Iglesiasu. </event>
      <event start="T1417-842" end="T1420-697">On je imel tudi eee r() delaye na, na, na ... </event>
      <event start="T1421-07" end="T496">Uuu, </event>
      <event start="T496" end="T1422-835">je rekel, </event>
      <event start="T1422-835" end="T497">je rekel: </event>
      <event start="T497" end="T498">"Crazy," </event>
      <event start="T498" end="T1427-086">pa je še dve minuti [nerazumljivo]. </event>
      <event start="T1427-086" end="T1428-453">Je tako. </event>
      <event start="T1429-622" end="T500">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T500" end="T501">pol četrtega, Kovak, greva pa na Mi2, k imajo tridesetletnico, </event>
      <event start="T501" end="T1433-387">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1433-387" end="T1435-281">Tako da bo kar, </event>
      <event start="T1435-281" end="T502">bo kar zanimivo, </event>
      <event start="T502" end="T1436-509">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1437-361" end="T503">Tako da nič, </event>
      <event start="T503" end="T504">glej, </event>
      <event start="T504" end="T505">se slišimo, </event>
      <event start="T505" end="T506">ne, </event>
      <event start="T506" end="T507">spet ob priliki, </event>
      <event start="T507" end="T1440-552">no, </event>
      <event start="T1440-552" end="T1441-067">pa drži se, </event>
      <event start="T1441-067" end="T1441-919">no. </event>
      <event start="T1442-969" end="T508">Dobro, </event>
      <event start="T508" end="T1444-217">ajde, živjo. </event>
      <event start="T1444-217" end="T1445-010">Bok. </event>
